    "An answer of \"Yes\" resulted in movement to the next question \"Have you used ChatGPT before the study?\"",
    "(Yes vs. No).",
    "An answer of \"No\" resulted in moving into the attitude scale questions (13 items), while the answer of \"yes\" resulted in moving into the attitude and usage scale questions altogether (25 items).",
    "The items comprising the constructs of TAME-ChatGPT is shown in (Appendix S1).",
    "Each scale item was assessed using a 5-point Likert scale, where \"agree\" corresponded to a score of 5, \"somewhat agree\" to 4, \"neutral/no opinion\" to 3, \"somewhat disagree\" to 2, and \"disagree\" to 1."
